    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Boil a kettle</span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Trim the\u00a0<strong>asparagus</strong>, discarding the woody ends</span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Chop the<strong>\u00a0asparagus tips</strong>\u00a0away from the stalks and set aside</span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Roughly chop the\u00a0<strong>stalks</strong></span></p> <p>\u00a0</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the\u00a0<strong>spaghetti</strong>\u00a0to a pot of<strong>\u00a0boiled water</strong>\u00a0with a generous pinch of\u00a0<strong>salt </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">and\u00a0</span>bring to the boil over a high heat</p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Once boiling,</span> cook for an initial 4-5 min\u00a0</p> <p>After 4-5 min add the <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">chopped\u00a0asparagus</span>\u00a0</strong>and cook for a further 4-5 min\u00a0or until <span class=\"text-highlight\">tender</span> with a slight bite</p> <p>Once cooked, drain and reserve a cup of the\u00a0<strong>starchy cooking water\u00a0</strong></p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">While the pasta is cooking, cut the <strong>red</strong>\u00a0<strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop \ufb01nely</span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Separate the<strong> white crab meat</strong> from the <strong>brown crab meat</strong> with a spoon (you'll use the white meat at the end!)</span></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half\u00a0</p> <p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot over a low heat with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil\u00a0</strong></p> <p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped chilli</strong>\u00a0(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 3-4 min until starting to soften</p> <p>Add the <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">Chinese rice w</span>ine</strong> and give <span class=\"text-highlight\">everything</span> a good mix up</p> <p>Add the <strong>brown crab meat</strong>\u00a0with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<span class=\"text-highlight\"> mix to combine</span> \u2013 this is your <strong>crab sauce\u00a0</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong> to the <strong>crab sauce</strong>\u00a0with <span class=\"text-highlight\">100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span></span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and the <strong>juice </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">of\u00a01/2\u00a0<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> </span><strong>lemon\u00a0</strong></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Give everything a good mix up until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta</span></p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</span></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Remove the pot</span> from the heat and gently stir through the <strong>white crab meat </strong>and\u00a0<strong>chopped parsley </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">\u2013 this is your<strong> crab, chilli &amp; lemon spaghetti</strong></span></p> <p>Chop the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simple-crab-chilli-and-lemon-spaghetti/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<span class=\"text-highlight\"> <strong>crab, chilli &amp; lemon spaghetti</strong></span> with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong> to the side</p> <p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Season\u00a0with a good grind</span> of <strong>black pepper</strong></p> <p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
